    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and offers a fantastic driving experience! It has been cared for responsibly, showing only the typical minor signs of use you'd expect from a reliable pre-owned car. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is perfectly suited for anyone looking for a dependable, high-quality ride without the brand-new price tag.",
