    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior paint has some noticeable fading on the hood and roof, along with a few small dings and scratches from regular use. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some minor staining, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape.",
