    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, which remains in impeccable showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing no discernible signs of wear, this unit represents the pinnacle of its class. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a standard of care that satisfies even the most exacting collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such distinguished provenance and flawless presentation.",
